Class CurvePointService

java.lang.Object
com.nnk.springboot.services.CurvePointService
@Service

    • getCurvePointById

      public CurvePoint getCurvePointById​(java.lang.Integer id)
      Get a curve point from its id.
      Parameters:
      id - The curve point id to get.
      Returns:
      An optional which may or may not contain the curve point. If a curve point is present, isPresent() returns true. If no curve point is present, the object is considered empty and isPresent() returns false.
